name: FINU
description: Formula Inu is a Decentralized Finance (DeFi) project on the Ethereum Blockchain. We fill the gap between the racing industry and web3. We are creating an ecosystem of multiple revenue streams generated from in-real-life and web3 business operations. Profits generated from our business operations revenue streams will be allocated to our holders via stablecoin-rewards, as well as to further develop and market the overall project operations.
